<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 12:12:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人即使热血沸腾也必须保持人性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-must-maintain-their-humanity-even-when-their-blood-boils/0000018b-1e18-d465-abbb-1ebe62c80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-must-maintain-their-humanity-even-when-their-blood-boils/0000018b-1e18-d465-abbb-1ebe62c80000</guid></item><item><title>超过一万名美国犹太人在联合国前集会表达对以色列的声援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/more-than-10-000-american-jews-express-solidarity-with-israel-at-rally-in-front-of-un/0000018b-1c9e-d08b-adef-1ffe20850000</link><description>这是自周六上午战争爆发以来为支持以色列举行的最大规模的国际集会，也是几十年来首次将如此大规模的美国犹太人聚集在一起</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/more-than-10-000-american-jews-express-solidarity-with-israel-at-rally-in-front-of-un/0000018b-1c9e-d08b-adef-1ffe20850000</guid></item><item><title>自哈马斯袭击以色列以来，法国报告了数十起反犹太主义行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-11/ty-article/france-reports-dozens-of-antisemitic-acts-since-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-1e40-d465-abbb-1ef6cceb0000</link><description>法国教育部长称，巴黎大区一名犹太学生遭到同学袭击，撕破了他的 T 恤</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:54:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-11/ty-article/france-reports-dozens-of-antisemitic-acts-since-hamas-attack-on-israel/0000018b-1e40-d465-abbb-1ef6cceb0000</guid></item><item><title>如何与您的孩子谈论以色列-加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</link><description>我们都在尽最大努力保护我们的孩子免受新闻和互联网上可怕的可怕图像的影响，但我们需要明白，即使是很小的孩子也能敏锐地意识到周围发生的事情。以下是有关如何解决这种情况的一些实用建议</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/how-to-talk-to-your-children-about-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-1b54-df31-a99f-7fd7f1430000</guid></item><item><title>“不是以色列国防军，也不是警察。一块金属在纳哈尔奥兹救了我、我的妻子和我们的孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</link><description>在大屠杀发生很久之后，数百名从纳哈尔奥兹基布兹获救的以色列人描述了恐惧，以及被遗弃的感觉。但他们想回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 09:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/not-the-idf-not-the-police-what-saved-my-family-in-nahal-oz-was-a-piece-of-metal/0000018b-1d7a-d2fc-a59f-dd7b0d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列援助组织将创伤专业知识带回家乡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</link><description>以色列援助团体帮助了世界各地偏远地区的灾难受害者，但现在，他们正在离家更近的地方运用他们的技能</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 08:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/bringing-trauma-expertise-full-circle-back-to-israel/0000018b-1d9d-d465-abbb-1dbfea960000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡推迟与甘茨就紧急战时政府问题举行会晤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-postpones-meeting-with-gantz-over-emergency-wartime-government/0000018b-1d9a-d465-abbb-1dbeac090000</link><description>两人定于周三会面。民族团结党消息人士称：“内塔尼亚胡正在拖延、拖延、拖延。首相没有表现出任何惊慌的迹象”</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 07:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-postpones-meeting-with-gantz-over-emergency-wartime-government/0000018b-1d9a-d465-abbb-1dbeac090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯正在交换囚犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/an-israel-hamas-prisoner-exchange-now/0000018b-1d77-d465-abbb-1df773680000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 06:59:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/an-israel-hamas-prisoner-exchange-now/0000018b-1d77-d465-abbb-1df773680000</guid></item><item><title>可怕的袭击开始五小时后，一颗卫星捕捉到了哈马斯在以色列的暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/five-hours-after-gruesome-attack-began-a-satellite-captured-hamas-atrocities-in-israel/0000018b-1d2f-d465-abbb-1dbf49fc0000</link><description>当地时间周六上午 11 点 31 分，欧洲航天局的一颗卫星飞过以色列上空，记录了哈马斯如何烧毁以色列房屋并屠杀数百名无辜平民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 06:07:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-11/ty-article-magazine/five-hours-after-gruesome-attack-began-a-satellite-captured-hamas-atrocities-in-israel/0000018b-1d2f-d465-abbb-1dbf49fc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙空袭哈马斯领导人，以色列死亡人数飙升至1,200人，2,400人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-live/1-200-israelis-killed-2-400-wounded-as-israel-targets-hamas-leaders-in-airstrikes/0000018b-1d16-d08b-adef-1ff68d470000</link><description>以色列和真主党在北部边境交火 ■ 至少 1,200 名以色列人死亡，2,400 人受伤 ■ 数十名外国人被杀、绑架 ■ 巴勒斯坦人称以色列空袭造成 950 人死亡、5,000 人受伤 ■ 以色列国防军：持有 1,500 具武装分子尸体，呼吁加沙人逃离飞往埃及</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 05:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article-live/1-200-israelis-killed-2-400-wounded-as-israel-targets-hamas-leaders-in-airstrikes/0000018b-1d16-d08b-adef-1ff68d470000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡，一个无法继续担任以色列总理的帮派头目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-a-gang-leader-who-cant-go-on-serving-as-israels-pm/0000018b-1b59-df31-a99f-7fdb49cc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 04:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-a-gang-leader-who-cant-go-on-serving-as-israels-pm/0000018b-1b59-df31-a99f-7fdb49cc0000</guid></item><item><title>这是政治炸药，所以他们不会让恐怖出现在电视上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/its-political-dynamite-so-theyll-keep-the-horror-off-tv/0000018b-1b56-d2fc-a59f-db5f67c80000</link><description>10 月 7 日的恐怖事件掌握在以色列公众的手机上，立即消除了他们对领导人的信任</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 03:27:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/its-political-dynamite-so-theyll-keep-the-horror-off-tv/0000018b-1b56-d2fc-a59f-db5f67c80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军加大对加沙的打击力度并准备地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-ramps-up-strikes-on-gaza-prepares-for-ground-invasion/0000018b-1b4c-d2fc-a59f-db5d8aee0000</link><description>在战争的第四天，在南部社区发现了 30 名失踪的以色列人；军队已通知50名俘虏的家属，死亡人数已达900人；拜登全力支持以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 01:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-ramps-up-strikes-on-gaza-prepares-for-ground-invasion/0000018b-1b4c-d2fc-a59f-db5d8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>恐怖事件过后，以色列现在必须决定接管加沙的问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-beefs-up-forces-but-to-what-end/0000018b-1b4d-df31-a99f-7fcfe0420000</link><description>哈马斯袭击带来的震惊开始消散，但以色列行动的目的仍然不明朗，无论是压制恐怖组织的军事能力还是推翻政权——这需要占领加沙</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 00:15:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-beefs-up-forces-but-to-what-end/0000018b-1b4d-df31-a99f-7fcfe0420000</guid></item><item><title>塔克·卡尔森质疑美国对以色列战争的支持——共和党会效仿吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/tucker-carlson-questions-u-s-support-for-israel-war-could-the-gop-follow/0000018b-19c2-dcc0-a3df-9de2ad700000</link><description>卡尔森反对共和党支持以色列对哈马斯进行自卫反击，这使他成为一个异类。但他巨大的影响力可能会让一些共和党人对以色列持更加怀疑的立场</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 23:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/tucker-carlson-questions-u-s-support-for-israel-war-could-the-gop-follow/0000018b-19c2-dcc0-a3df-9de2ad700000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学学生支持的指责以色列暴力的声明引发强烈反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/statement-blaming-israel-for-violence-endorsed-by-harvard-students-unleashes-backlash/0000018b-1a43-d465-abbb-1ef795fc0000</link><description>哈佛大学数十个学生组织签署的一份声明，被认为使哈马斯屠杀近千名以色列人合法化，在这所常春藤盟校引发轩然大波</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 20:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/statement-blaming-israel-for-violence-endorsed-by-harvard-students-unleashes-backlash/0000018b-1a43-d465-abbb-1ef795fc0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：美国支持以色列对哈马斯“纯粹、纯粹的邪恶”做出“迅速、果断、压倒性”的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-supports-israeli-overwhelming-response-against-hamas-pure-evil/0000018b-1af4-d08b-adef-1ff6dda30000</link><description>拜登说，这次袭击呼应了“千年来的反犹太主义和对犹太人的种族灭绝”，并重申美国“与以色列站在一起”。他还警告任何考虑利用这种情况的国家或组织：“不要这样做。”不&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 19:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-supports-israeli-overwhelming-response-against-hamas-pure-evil/0000018b-1af4-d08b-adef-1ff6dda30000</guid></item><item><title>“所以全世界都知道发生了什么”：卡法阿扎基布兹的屠杀现场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/so-the-world-knows-what-happened-the-scene-of-slaughter-at-kibbutz-kfar-azza/0000018b-1aa1-df31-a99f-7fe3eae50000</link><description>800 名以色列人居住在卡法阿扎 (Kfar Azza)，这是加沙城可见范围内的一个基布兹。现在，他们中的许多人都只是数字：死亡、受伤、失踪、被俘。参观大屠杀以来最大的犹太人屠杀现场</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 19:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/so-the-world-knows-what-happened-the-scene-of-slaughter-at-kibbutz-kfar-azza/0000018b-1aa1-df31-a99f-7fe3eae50000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙边境附近的以色列基布兹躲避恐怖分子的三十名失踪者获救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/thirty-missing-who-hid-from-terrorists-at-israeli-kibbutz-are-rescued/0000018b-1aae-d2fc-a59f-dbbfc0290000</link><description>周六大批哈马斯恐怖分子从加沙入侵后，这 16 名以色列人和 14 名泰国人躲藏起来，周一晚间警方收到有关他们下落的信息后获救。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 18:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/thirty-missing-who-hid-from-terrorists-at-israeli-kibbutz-are-rescued/0000018b-1aae-d2fc-a59f-dbbfc0290000</guid></item><item><title>392名美国众议院议员提出支持以色列对抗哈马斯“野蛮”袭击的决议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/392-u-s-house-reps-back-israel-against-barbaric-hamas-attacks/0000018b-1aa7-dcc0-a3df-9ea778210000</link><description>广泛的支持，只有 43 名众议院议员作为最初的共同提案国缺失，反映出两党对以色列的支持几乎是史无前例的，而此时华盛顿也许从未陷入过这样的政治僵局</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/392-u-s-house-reps-back-israel-against-barbaric-hamas-attacks/0000018b-1aa7-dcc0-a3df-9ea778210000</guid></item></channel></rss>